{"tid":1925852,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[尋找苦主] 過完數即block人間蒸發走數！！","createTime":"2020-03-14T16:42:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-19T06:52:18.000Z","uid":177214,"like":9,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"7beab337dcd11a07a10e6a6710f4e75599bb2546","tid":1925852,"uid":177214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T16:42:32.000Z","msg":"認住尼個人！！！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/r42ZdmV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fr42ZdmV.png&h=60885914&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n詳細係我係fb鞋谷徵鞋，比尼個人inbox<br />\n傾左一大輪，講好哂價錢比哂相約交收既時候<br />\n聲稱自己住澳門，近排過境面交唔方便..<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kOTxyFH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkOTxyFH.png&h=570b93de&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n得出結論係順豐寄比我，我當時覺得過數再寄，好冇保障，say左no，對話如下<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6uCZdG8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6uCZdG8.png&h=35d71eff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後都應成左先過一半數收到貨過<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ygXN63t.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FygXN63t.png&h=fb98a3dc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n過完數之後，做戲做全套，問埋郵寄詳情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JaYd2Ez.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJaYd2Ez.png&h=ec848e45&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n對話就到尼到，跟住就秒block左我，完全聯絡唔到<br />\n宜家心頭上得佢個轉數快no. 同hsbc 戶口<br />\n已經打算去報案，亦都係希望當時人睇到主動聯絡反還反錢（雖然冇乜可能）<br />\n<br />\n亦都想靠連登尼個平台睇下搵唔搵到其他比佢呃左既人同苦主，睇下有冇同路人<br />\n一齊有報案no.，相信警察個邊做野都會快d<br />\n<br />\n預左比各位屌傻仔，屌細力d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但我最重要既想睇下宜家有冇咩方法可以做到，唔想再有下個受害者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b10865d7a4d8180fee7f0042080ee77404471e1","tid":1925852,"uid":177214,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T16:55:27.000Z","msg":"係到放沉好快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f07b019c1e4fa7920f57707283ae195eac0f5ca","tid":1925852,"uid":49128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T16:57:54.000Z","msg":"吹水台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有冇多d佢相資料？"},{"pid":"daf7348b0d19192f9fb66a9aa796de078cd2f6f6","tid":1925852,"uid":177214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4f07b019c1e4fa7920f57707283ae195eac0f5ca","tid":1925852,"uid":49128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T16:57:54.000Z","msg":"吹水台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有冇多d佢相資料？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T17:04:51.000Z","msg":"得咁多...因為個時冇諗到結果會咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n想cap圖既時候已經被block<br />\n完全Search 唔到"},{"pid":"fad3e3e2891ff565055ba71d6af8b46947f0b711","tid":1925852,"uid":177214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4f07b019c1e4fa7920f57707283ae195eac0f5ca","tid":1925852,"uid":49128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T16:57:54.000Z","msg":"吹水台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有冇多d佢相資料？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T17:05:21.000Z","msg":"應該放咩台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e6e41b6bba03c681ca0ff6c3a6efdbc9887ed21","tid":1925852,"uid":224281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T17:06:10.000Z","msg":"幫你捱"},{"pid":"20583071a0683b34865940c66c07a2419bd550c9","tid":1925852,"uid":224281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5e6e41b6bba03c681ca0ff6c3a6efdbc9887ed21","tid":1925852,"uid":224281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T17:06:10.000Z","msg":"幫你捱"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T17: